TITLE Resolution Function of 3T2 obtained from  Si3N4 (lambda=1.2253 angstroms)
! To be used with IRESO=1 in FullProf.2k (version > 1.6)
JOBT CW Neutrons
!     Lambda1    Lambda2   Ratio(I2/I1)
WAVE  1.225300   1.225300      0.0
!    NPROF    Shape1    Shape2   Shape3
PROF    7        0.0       0.0      0.0
!  Cos(2thM)^2 for polarization = 0 for neutrons
CTHM  0.0
!     2theta-min   step   2theta-max
THRG     2.0       0.05      125.00
!          Uins     Vins      Wins      Xins      Yins      Zins
UVWXYZ  0.275264  -0.393932   0.216173   0.00000   0.01140     0.000
